":"2019-06-22T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"香港警队，日日为香港治安尽心尽力，维持香港维持香港繁荣美好风景！<br />\n近日流传他们滥用暴力，他们受了太多屈辱。为咗还警队一个清白，我们需要支持特区政府成立独立调查委员会！费事啲人话佢哋作贼心虚！<br />\n用司法还他们一个&ldquo;公正的评价&rdquo;！<br />\n警队是仁慈的，警队是清白的！<br />\n<br />\n**支持成立独立调查委员会**！<br />\n<br />\n#支持请广传"},{"pid":"f64a1a3fe181e14b2025b50b9fa8b7e4bd68696c","tid":1250154,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBhoGKh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBhoGKh.png&h=60453465&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6m18SQ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6m18SQ1.png&h=51a0e24b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"036c1db9c546f6e55fbbee49ff49e1478a182b20","tid":1250154,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/22/5EbBtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F5EbBtJ.jpg&h=526834e7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"83997e5be2e721385630bc97e93d71a8be6f6af5","tid":1250154,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"036c1db9c546f6e55fbbee49ff49e1478a182b20","tid":1250154,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/22/5EbBtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F22%2F5EbBtJ.jpg&h=526834e7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdsjZwM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdsjZwM.png&h=b10dba91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4916ba316beef8d7974077a4ef8d8dc54e62c149","tid":1250154,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"根本就係警方阻住救人"},